				<p>*cry* it went all wrong!! I had the same problem those couple people had from the start: once i&#8217;d added the flour my dough became a dry crumbly mess!  I tried to salvage it by adding in some egg white to make it come together, but even though I added 3/8 c. I think I should have put more because the cookies were dry.</p>
